}
SalesRep --> Createanewcontactrecordforapotentialclient
Contact --> Createanewcontactrecordforapotentialclient
SalesRep --> Loganactivityagainstacontactoraccount
Contact --> Loganactivityagainstacontactoraccount
SalesRep --> Createanewsalesopportunityandtrackitsvalueandstageinthepipeline
Manager --> Viewadashboardofthecurrentsalespipelineandtotalrevenueforecast
